        "  tiny    fastest, lowest accuracy, ~75 MB\n"
        "  base    fast, low accuracy, ~150 MB\n"
        "  small   moderate, ~500 MB\n"
        "  medium  good accuracy, slower, ~1.5 GB\n"
        "  large   highest accuracy, slowest, ~3 GB  (default)\n"
        "  turbo   large-v3-turbo: large quality, ~5× faster, ~1.5 GB\n"
